First of all absolutely loved her skin 🤩 
This is my version of a Soft Contour Application - what’s your preferences for contour ? 
I like to alternate between powder contour/bronzers or a cream product to get my desired finish. Always best to start with minimal product and build up from there if needed. If in the event I happen to apply too much I find that going back in with my foundation brush helps blend that product into the skin more. And then I go in with my setting powder to lock everything in 😍
